    <h1>Demand-Side Platform (DSP)</h1>
    <p class="description">Software advertisers use to buy digital ad inventory across many exchanges through <strong>real-time bidding</strong>. Powers <strong>90%+ of US display ad spend</strong> and gives access to open-web inventory that Google and Meta don't touch.</p>
